    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra into your hand and mouth, and slowly breathe out a small, solid stream of fire that shapes itself into a sword. The weapon counts as a chisagatana, and attacks made with it are touch attacks dealing 1d6 fire damage, +1 per two levels (maximum +8). Since the blade is not material, you cannot add your Strength bonus to damage with the blade. The sword can be used to ignite combustible materials.</p>\n\n\n\n",
